Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.08,0:21:33.51,Shirobako_Main,ema,0000,0000,0000,,Falo de seu objetivo final.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.51,0:21:35.07,Shirobako_Main,aoi,0000,0000,0000,,Objetivo final?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.65,0:21:42.82,Shirobako_Main,aoi,0000,0000,0000,,Não sei. Qual será meu objetivo final?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.44,0:21:46.35,Shirobako_Main,ema,0000,0000,0000,,Preciso voltar ao trabalho.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.81,0:21:48.41,Shirobako_Main,ema,0000,0000,0000,,Como isto depois, está bem?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.39,0:22:04.19,Shirobako_Main,iguchi,0000,0000,0000,,Opa!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.92,0:22:06.73,Shirobako_Main,iguchi,0000,0000,0000,,Que perigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.22,0:22:10.11,Shirobako_Main,iguchi,0000,0000,0000,,Isto é seu, Yasuharacchi?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.66,0:22:11.53,Shirobako_Main,iguchi,0000,0000,0000,,Quer de volta?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.79,0:22:17.78,Shirobako_Main,iguchi,0000,0000,0000,,Então é meu.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.64,0:22:20.64,Shirobako_Main,iguchi,0000,0000,0000,,Que foi?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.86,0:22:23.29,Shirobako_Main,kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Pronto!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.63,0:22:26.75,Shirobako_Main,midor,0000,0000,0000,,Nossa! Parece uma pessoa\N que vai a um casamento!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.75,0:22:29.33,Shirobako_Main,kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Casamento? Boa! Vamos?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.33,0:22:30.71,Shirobako_Main,midori,0000,0000,0000,,Foi convidada?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.71,0:22:31.89,Shirobako_Main,kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Não.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.89,0:22:32.41,Shirobako_Main,mdiro,0000,0000,0000,,Hein?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.41,0:22:34.01,Shirobako_Main,kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Experimente um também, Rii-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.52,0:22:36.34,Shirobako_Main,midori,0000,0000,0000,,Eu não compro roupas assim.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.34,0:22:38.17,Shirobako_Main,kaori,0000,0000,0000,,É só para experimentar.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.17,0:22:40.68,Shirobako_Main,midori,0000,0000,0000,,Hã? Kao-chan-neisan? Espere...
